reviews.text: I would like to give 4.5 star instead. The Panda has a relatively room in Hong Kong Standard. The rooms are still under renovation progressively. Some dated rooms surely need to be improved. The refurbished rooms look good. The location is convenient is good and have free shuttle to downtown. Staff is nice.
Place is well-maintained and just a walk away from the MRT station. Bus stop is directly outside the hotel which makes commuting much easier. Friendly staff and very accommodating to our needs.

Good location with all amenities in the same block,  underground station Tsuen wan stop is easier to get to. Room is good size, clean all house keepers are very helpful, polite and professional.  We felt our pillows were a little uncomfortable they should have offer more choices and our room window does not opens.
Good hotel rooms are small.convenient location metro is near by and few food outlets are also nearby like pizza hut McDonald's.free shuttle to City center is great value add.
Great shopping and right below the hotel. Close to metro station. Good prices on rooms. Free pick up and dropping to city daily.

reviews.text: 不錯😊
高質數美食和服務👍

好伏！
從來冇試過check out前會俾人問使唔使洗衫！Horrible and unacceptable experience!
Their room attendant will press your doorbell several times to make sure they can ask you : do you need laundry service? I just stay for one night, the check out time is 12 noon. They ask me at 10am, when I doing a bath!!!

I have never encountered this before! I travel a lot! Even though in China or other developing countries, I have never encountered this before! I am so angry.I am the local, I book a local hotel for 1 to 2 nights for relaxation frequently.

Besides,  after I met this, I read some comments, some travelers also met this. They put the no disturb sign on the door, but their room still cleaned! 

If you care about this issue, please think before you make any of reservation.

按左幾次門鐘，嗰時係早上10點，咁弱智拍門問人使唔使洗衫，嗰時我沖緊涼！咁樣做法，會唔會又拍門問洗唔洗room service 送餐？ 又拍門問使唔使加廁紙？
唔該你哋開會通知晒佢哋唔好再咁做，係冇可能發生呢啲咁嘅事，咁樣趕人走？心情被完全破壞！之後睇返comment，幾個渠道啦，都有提及咁嘅情況！
自助餐不錯，價值合理，到荃灣巿中心吃吃喝喝都方便，不用乘車都可以，就算乘的士都很近便，乘坐港鐵出九龍亦方便容易。酒店附近又有多所禮拜堂，荃灣宣道會，荃灣浸信會，基督中心堂，方便遊客旅客在上教堂參加主日崇拜聚會，洗滌心靈，持守聚會。

reviews.text: 都好味道🍷❤️☕️

Pizza hut真心係信心保證，一諗唔到食咩就會食呢間😂

沙律好味，好多蟹子😍 菜都好新鮮。

加錢既酥皮龍蝦🦞湯。

拉絲pizza🤣 啲fd問我淨係食一個pizza夠唔夠飽，我心諗點會唔夠呀，勁大
呢個肉醬意粉值得一提，我兩個fd都叫左，但成品好唔同😂 一個好正常好好味，一個水lel lel，好似食緊湯米線咁🤣 但個味當然都係好，懷疑未焗夠時間就拎出黎 😂

講開時間，繁忙時間出餐有少少慢同亂，但店員態度都好好👏🏻

會員積分又儲夠喇！送8隻雞翼正呀！
大窩口熊貓酒店呢一間，食物冇問題，但係啲員工嘅工作態度就古古怪怪。
父親節取消一人set lunch,對我沒影響，但有想過今天要一人來吃飯的顧客，他們的感受嗎？
只要繼續唔係CCTVB落廣告，都會繼續幫襯佢

reviews.text:
Fist come first serve base .(full class now)熊貓學堂Nice free summer Panda school.
Nice, big variety of shops!

The Panda Hotel has been around for many years and is still a wonderful food and service experience. I have personally visited the Panda probably more than 150 times since the 1980s. People said it would not work as it was not in the city. TRUST ME IT HAS and continues to do so.
Visit,you won't be disappointed.

This place has plenty of restaurants, making it easy to find food here. The food ranging from Japanese, Western, Koreans, Chinese, including local food. It is connected with Panda Hotel and minutes away from MTR station, making it easily accessible.

Convinient  if you are a tourist this mall is good i recommend to book panda hotel as well since you just take the elevator and there will be a lot of things to eat but nothing much to do here they have shoes and clothes as well for sale
Nice place. Lot of things to do. You can spend a whole day here. Shopping , eating and more to do.
